@Repeatable allows the same **annotation** to be applied multiple times to the same element.
@Repeatable requires a "container annotation" to be specified.
The container annotation must have a value() element whose type is an [[array]] of the repeatable annotation.
The @Retention and @Target of the container annotation must match those of the repeatable annotation.

